1
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:55,120
Boss Xiao,

2
00:00:55,521 --> 00:00:57,001
the seal's design

3
00:00:57,321 --> 00:00:58,521
is quite unique.

4
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:02,601
It's a legendary auspicious beast

5
00:01:03,120 --> 00:01:04,001
known as Red Heart.

6
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:06,041
To protect peace,

7
00:01:06,281 --> 00:01:07,440
it was wounded by a great demon,

8
00:01:07,641 --> 00:01:09,080
and its soul scattered

9
00:01:09,121 --> 00:01:10,001
to unknown places.

10
00:01:10,401 --> 00:01:11,360
Strange things

11
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:13,041
happened in my shop for a while.

12
00:01:13,401 --> 00:01:15,201
Thanks to the advice of Xu Qinglai,

13
00:01:15,720 --> 00:01:17,360
I began to worship this beast.

14
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:18,600
Since then,

15
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,561
nothing has happened.

16
00:01:24,001 --> 00:01:25,160
No trace?

17
00:01:26,401 --> 00:01:29,401
Does Boss Xiao know anything else about the Red Heart?

18
00:01:30,761 --> 00:01:34,121
Rumor has it, the Red Heart has been gathering its pieces for a long time.

19
00:01:34,160 --> 00:01:36,761
It has almost collected all the pieces

20
00:01:36,761 --> 00:01:37,841
and merged them into one.

21
00:01:37,841 --> 00:01:40,921
Now only the most important piece is missing.

22
00:01:42,041 --> 00:01:43,121
It's called

23
00:01:43,641 --> 00:01:45,240
the Water Cloud Rhinoceros.

24
00:01:46,160 --> 00:01:47,440
Where is the Water Cloud Rhinoceros?

25
00:01:48,001 --> 00:01:49,761
There's a painting demon on the Rhinoceros Moon Mountain,

26
00:01:50,041 --> 00:01:51,681
who records the stories of the world.

27
00:01:53,921 --> 00:01:54,880
Don't worry.

28
00:01:55,201 --> 00:01:57,641
If you're interested in these stories,

29
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:59,641
come with me to the backyard

30
00:02:00,281 --> 00:02:01,681
after the painting is finished.

31
00:02:02,001 --> 00:02:04,520
I'll tell you

32
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:06,641
the strange stories.

33
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:14,561
Please tell me your name.

34
00:02:15,001 --> 00:02:18,401
I'll write it on the painting.

35
00:02:27,001 --> 00:02:27,801
Meng Li.

36
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:39,121
So you're the one forging the paintings.

37
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,401
You'd better behave yourself.

38
00:02:48,401 --> 00:02:49,720
Otherwise,

39
00:02:50,281 --> 00:02:53,361
I'll distribute these explicit paintings

40
00:02:55,401 --> 00:02:57,281
and ruin your reputation.

41
00:03:01,241 --> 00:03:01,920
Shopkeeper,

42
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,001
Prince Xian is here.

43
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:08,480
Take this woman away.

44
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:09,320
Yes.

45
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:10,241
Just in time.

46
00:03:10,841 --> 00:03:12,160
Let me see

47
00:03:12,521 --> 00:03:14,880
what other secrets this place holds.

48
00:03:18,961 --> 00:03:19,640
Go in.

49
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,121
I'm sorry for not greeting you.

50
00:03:35,121 --> 00:03:35,920
I hope

51
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:37,040
Your Highness will forgive me.

52
00:03:39,681 --> 00:03:42,200
What are you here for?

53
00:03:43,121 --> 00:03:45,281
I heard you have many portraits of women.

54
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,001
I also want to see them.

55
00:03:51,961 --> 00:03:53,401
Your Highness,

56
00:03:53,561 --> 00:03:55,281
if you come here for this,

57
00:03:55,281 --> 00:03:56,920
then you've come to the right place.

58
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:03,200
Your Highness, please take a look.

59
00:04:03,401 --> 00:04:04,841
Please pick freely.

60
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:05,640
I

61
00:04:05,961 --> 00:04:07,401
can arrange it.

62
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,080
[What is she doing here?]

63
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:23,001
Your Highness, do you like this girl?

64
00:04:23,921 --> 00:04:24,760
It's okay.

65
00:04:25,121 --> 00:04:26,361
Turn the pages.

66
00:04:26,361 --> 00:04:28,601
It's more exciting.

67
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,200
Shen Que.

68
00:04:31,681 --> 00:04:32,640
Destroy it.

69
00:04:33,041 --> 00:04:34,161
You must destroy it.

70
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:38,721
Are you satisfied?

71
00:04:40,481 --> 00:04:42,200
If you need anything,

72
00:04:42,241 --> 00:04:43,520
I can arrange it.

73
00:04:45,481 --> 00:04:46,681
I just ask that Your Highness

74
00:04:47,041 --> 00:04:48,561
will promote me in the future.

75
00:04:48,561 --> 00:04:49,960
Is she here?

76
00:04:50,361 --> 00:04:51,161
Of course.

77
00:04:51,681 --> 00:04:52,561
Your Highness, please wait a moment.

78
00:04:53,001 --> 00:04:55,001
I'll go arrange it right away.

79
00:05:13,161 --> 00:05:13,960
Water.

80
00:05:14,801 --> 00:05:16,121
The water is clean.

81
00:05:24,121 --> 00:05:24,921
Thank you.

82
00:05:29,361 --> 00:05:30,241
You

83
00:05:30,361 --> 00:05:32,080
were also tricked in by that painter?

84
00:05:34,121 --> 00:05:34,721
Yes.

85
00:05:35,561 --> 00:05:36,921
He tricked me into the Chunbugui

86
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,520
by painting.

87
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:40,241
He forged those disgusting things

88
00:05:40,361 --> 00:05:41,001
to

89
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:42,241
extort money.

90
00:05:42,241 --> 00:05:43,161
I couldn't get it,

91
00:05:43,161 --> 00:05:44,481
so he locked me up here.

92
00:05:44,481 --> 00:05:45,921
He also told my father and brother.

93
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:47,601
They thought I was shameful,

94
00:05:47,601 --> 00:05:49,200
so they cut off the relationship.

95
00:05:49,361 --> 00:05:50,320
There are

96
00:05:50,601 --> 00:05:52,440
many girls in the same situation

97
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:53,721
who share my fate.

98
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:28,801
Your Highness,

99
00:06:29,681 --> 00:06:30,440
this is the girl

100
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,520
you have taken a fancy to.

101
00:06:37,601 --> 00:06:39,320
She is just as beautiful as the painting,

102
00:06:40,241 --> 00:06:41,361
radiant and charming.

103
00:06:43,041 --> 00:06:44,760
Why don't you pay your respects to Prince Xian?

104
00:06:45,241 --> 00:06:47,601
You are more debauched

105
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,481
than I imagined.

106
00:06:51,601 --> 00:06:52,481
Your Highness, please spare me.

107
00:06:52,481 --> 00:06:53,041
This...

108
00:06:53,121 --> 00:06:54,561
This isn't what I said.

109
00:06:54,801 --> 00:06:55,601
It's fine.

110
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:59,241
I like sharp-tongued women.

111
00:06:59,241 --> 00:06:59,681
Good.

112
00:07:05,361 --> 00:07:07,080
Pour wine for His Highness.

113
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,280
Serve him well.

114
00:07:10,161 --> 00:07:11,601
You want to cling to power.

115
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,721
Why don't you serve him yourself?

116
00:07:14,601 --> 00:07:15,481
How dare you!

117
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:26,400
No one has ever treated me like this.

118
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:28,200
What?

119
00:07:28,241 --> 00:07:29,760
You claim to

120
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,721
dedicate yourself to demon hunting.

121
00:07:32,121 --> 00:07:33,280
Yet you still have time

122
00:07:33,481 --> 00:07:34,960
to come here for pleasure?

123
00:07:35,601 --> 00:07:37,200
I came here

124
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:39,681
only to find a portrait.

125
00:07:40,601 --> 00:07:42,840
This studio specializes in portraits of women.

126
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:45,361
This person uses this as an excuse

127
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:47,121
to lure people into the Spring Never Returns.

128
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:49,760
Forging private portraits to blackmail.

129
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,561
You...

130
00:07:51,561 --> 00:07:52,601
You're talking nonsense.

131
00:07:52,601 --> 00:07:53,320
I didn't.

132
00:07:54,041 --> 00:07:55,760
Then I'm very curious

133
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:57,200
how did you get in here?

134
00:07:57,880 --> 00:07:59,161
Were you tricked in as well?

135
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:04,161
Your Highness, you are aware of this filthy business,

136
00:08:04,161 --> 00:08:05,361
yet you do not eradicate it.

137
00:08:05,361 --> 00:08:07,361
Could it be that you are colluding with this person,

138
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:09,640
planning to do harm to the women

139
00:08:10,161 --> 00:08:11,320
imprisoned in the dungeon?

140
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:15,561
There is actually a dungeon

141
00:08:15,561 --> 00:08:17,041
specifically for imprisoning women?

142
00:08:17,041 --> 00:08:18,400
How dare you!

143
00:08:19,161 --> 00:08:20,200
Your...

144
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:20,801
Your Highness,

145
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:23,041
don't just listen to her side of the story.

146
00:08:23,361 --> 00:08:24,561
It was those women

147
00:08:24,721 --> 00:08:25,400
who forced me

148
00:08:25,561 --> 00:08:27,041
to paint those albums for them.

149
00:08:31,601 --> 00:08:32,241
Look,

150
00:08:32,561 --> 00:08:33,280
these paintings

151
00:08:33,561 --> 00:08:35,400
were all requested by them.

152
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:38,241
How dare you!

153
00:08:38,241 --> 00:08:39,081
What do you want?

154
00:08:39,241 --> 00:08:40,800
How many innocent women

155
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:44,081
were abandoned by their families because of your forged portraits,

156
00:08:44,441 --> 00:08:45,560
and ended up in the brothels.

157
00:08:47,081 --> 00:08:48,201
Some even

158
00:08:48,481 --> 00:08:50,121
took their own lives

159
00:08:50,121 --> 00:08:51,081
to protect their name.

160
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:53,721
You killed people with just a few strokes.

161
00:08:54,001 --> 00:08:55,721
You are more vicious than the executioner.

162
00:09:01,601 --> 00:09:04,201
Is he the Utmost Evil One?

163
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:08,441
Fine.

164
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:11,760
I'll give him to you as an initiation gift.

165
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:26,841
Does it hurt?

166
00:09:27,321 --> 00:09:28,841
Do you know how many innocent girls

167
00:09:29,001 --> 00:09:30,241
lost their young lives

168
00:09:30,241 --> 00:09:32,081
because of your white silk?

169
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,280
Your Highness,

170
00:09:33,481 --> 00:09:34,321
she's a witch.

171
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:35,721
Please kill her.

172
00:09:35,841 --> 00:09:36,920
Save me, Your Highness.

173
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,040
Your Highness,

174
00:09:38,361 --> 00:09:40,280
I'll give you anything you want.

175
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:42,361
You'll give me anything I want?

176
00:09:43,481 --> 00:09:44,121
Alright.

177
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:46,481
I want you to apologize to those women.

178
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:48,201
I... I was wrong.

179
00:09:48,441 --> 00:09:49,601
I'll never do it again.

180
00:09:49,601 --> 00:09:51,361
I'll be more careful in the future

181
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:53,841
and won't cause you any more trouble.

182
00:09:54,121 --> 00:09:55,361
You show no remorse.

183
00:09:56,001 --> 00:09:56,760
You only show weakness

184
00:09:57,040 --> 00:09:58,640
because you know you're about to die.

185
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:00,040
You destroyed their lives

186
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,520
with just a paintbrush,

187
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:03,081
leaving them with no way to defend themselves.

188
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,121
Fine.

189
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:06,601
I'll seal your mouth now,

190
00:10:07,241 --> 00:10:09,081
so you can feel their despair.

191
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:30,160
How do you feel now?

192
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:32,001
What are your thoughts?

193
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:35,961
You can't speak,

194
00:10:37,201 --> 00:10:38,441
just like them.

195
00:10:38,441 --> 00:10:39,520
They can't defend themselves,

196
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:41,481
and can only endure the false accusations.

197
00:10:42,361 --> 00:10:43,841
Since you show no remorse,

198
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:45,721
then you don't deserve to live.

199
00:11:02,680 --> 00:11:04,001
I thought Your Highness

200
00:11:04,241 --> 00:11:06,160
only harbored deep hatred for our clan.

201
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:07,400
I didn't expect you to be

202
00:11:07,961 --> 00:11:09,201
merciless towards mortals as well.

203
00:11:16,920 --> 00:11:18,800
I am clear in my heart about what is right and wrong.

204
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:22,001
Such evil-doers

205
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:25,961
shouldn't be allowed to harm the innocent.

206
00:11:35,081 --> 00:11:36,001
Speak up.

207
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:37,800
What's with the hesitation?

208
00:11:38,001 --> 00:11:40,560
They say those who fight the righteous are demons.

209
00:11:41,201 --> 00:11:42,040
Who knew

210
00:11:42,481 --> 00:11:44,601
demons could also hate evil?

211
00:11:45,441 --> 00:11:46,400
This world

212
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:47,680
has both good

213
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:49,121
and bad.

214
00:11:49,721 --> 00:11:51,241
Pixies are the same.

215
00:11:51,841 --> 00:11:53,241
Only the ignorant

216
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:55,121
believe one side of the story.

217
00:11:55,121 --> 00:11:56,040
If pixies are so good,

218
00:11:56,201 --> 00:11:57,601
why not turn

219
00:11:57,920 --> 00:11:59,760
those weak women into pixies too?

220
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:01,441
Give them the power to protect themselves.

221
00:12:01,560 --> 00:12:02,560
Turning humans into pixies

222
00:12:02,680 --> 00:12:04,040
is a painful process.

223
00:12:04,481 --> 00:12:05,280
Besides,

224
00:12:05,481 --> 00:12:07,201
the abusers should be the ones

225
00:12:07,201 --> 00:12:07,920
suffering, not them.

226
00:12:09,961 --> 00:12:11,280
You knew it would hurt,

227
00:12:11,601 --> 00:12:12,800
yet you turned me into a pixie.

228
00:12:13,001 --> 00:12:14,880
And now you're here acting all noble.

229
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:16,721
How utterly hypocritical!

230
00:12:17,081 --> 00:12:19,841
You show mercy to a woman you've known just one day.

231
00:12:19,920 --> 00:12:21,081
Why not to me?

232
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:24,001
Don't you know what you've done?

233
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:25,400
You killed my closest friends,

234
00:12:25,400 --> 00:12:26,361
slaughtered my clan.

235
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:28,361
All the pain you're in is what you deserve.

236
00:12:28,361 --> 00:12:29,160
You should endure it.

237
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:30,201
Since you're so cruel to me,

238
00:12:31,001 --> 00:12:32,640
why keep me by your side?

239
00:12:35,961 --> 00:12:37,640
The nightmares you absorbed

240
00:12:38,321 --> 00:12:40,001
were for my use.

241
00:12:40,961 --> 00:12:42,481
That's why I won't kill you.

242
00:12:44,481 --> 00:12:46,321
Where can you go?

243
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:48,800
The world is so big,

244
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:51,560
but there's no place for you anymore.
